{"title":"雨","authors":["孙昕晨"],"dates":[{"year":1998,"month":6,"day":5}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"雨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孙昕晨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雨来了，这突如其"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来的一掌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把兔子松散的筋骨集"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"合起来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雨，撒蹄飞奔的雨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"骑在兔子背上的雨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比兔子跑得更快的雨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"压低了整个天空"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雨召唤着我们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大地上新鲜的部分"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一切事物的根"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凸现，裸露"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雨刺激着这些尽情开"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"放的花朵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"直到它无力回答你的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"问候"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赏雨的人躲在暗处"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风雨揪住了他的眼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"睛、嘴巴"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像这些庄稼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被一次次搂紧，又一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"株株分开"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"语言、目光、亲切的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"肌肤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来自土地深处的激情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请抓住机会交换你们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"的财富"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哗哗的雨水往低处流"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"流过祖先的额头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再往下，就是我们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"内心，一片空荡荡的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"峡谷"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":11,"page_end":11}